msgctxt "sn55.16:0.2"
msgid "2. Rājakārāmavagga "
msgstr "2. A Thousand Nuns "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 16. Paṭhamamittāmaccasutta → mittāmaccasuttaṃ (bj) | mittenāmaccā 1 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn55.16:0.3"
msgid "16. Paṭhamamittāmaccasutta "
msgstr "16. Friends and Colleagues (1st) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.365, sc1
msgctxt "sn55.16:1.1"
msgid "“Ye te, bhikkhave, anukampeyyātha, ye ca sotabbaṃ maññeyyuṃ—mittā vā amaccā vā ñātī vā sālohitā vā—te, bhikkhave, catūsu sotāpattiyaṅgesu samādapetabbā, nivesetabbā, patiṭṭhāpetabbā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, those who you have sympathy for, and those worth listening to—friends and colleagues, relatives and family—should be encouraged, supported, and established in the four factors of stream-entry. "

msgctxt "sn55.16:1.2"
msgid "Katamesu catūsu? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn55.16:1.3"
msgid "Buddhe aveccappasāde samādapetabbā, nivesetabbā, patiṭṭhāpetabbā—"
msgstr "Experiential confidence in the Buddha … "

msgctxt "sn55.16:1.4"
msgid "itipi so bhagavā … pe … satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavāti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn55.16:1.5"
msgid "Dhamme … pe … "
msgstr "the teaching … "

msgctxt "sn55.16:1.6"
msgid "saṃghe … pe … "
msgstr "the Saṅgha … "

msgctxt "sn55.16:1.7"
msgid "ariyakantesu sīlesu samādapetabbā, nivesetabbā, patiṭṭhāpetabbā akhaṇḍesu … pe … samādhisaṃvattanikesu. "
msgstr "And the ethical conduct loved by the noble ones … leading to immersion. "

msgctxt "sn55.16:1.8"
msgid "Ye te, bhikkhave, anukampeyyātha, ye ca sotabbaṃ maññeyyuṃ—mittā vā amaccā vā ñātī vā sālohitā vā—te, bhikkhave, imesu catūsu sotāpattiyaṅgesu samādapetabbā, nivesetabbā, patiṭṭhāpetabbā”ti. "
msgstr "Those who you have sympathy for, and those worth listening to—friends and colleagues, relatives and family—should be encouraged, supported, and established in these four factors of stream-entry.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn55.16:1.9"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

